Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: central radio north west
des:
With the official Central Radio Skill, you can hear your favorite radio right now on Alexa! 

Central Radio is bringing back real LOCAL radio for the people of Lancashire and the North West. You'll find none of that Manchester or London malarkey here, just information and music that matters to the people of our county.

Listen live, catch up with station news or check local and national news headlines. Wondering what the weather has in store for the next few days? You'll find that too!
